ss=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">ι</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">k</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">→₀</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">R</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"n\">f</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">embDomain</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">&lt;|</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">sigmaMk</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">k</span>\n</code></pre></div>",
